name: Experiment Or Die #31
description: Yearlong project to create a new collage every day using my years of photos and personal assets. This marks the end of the first month of designs for Experiment or Die. I'm still feeling my way through the NFT space but I've made it a month without missing a day, had some moderate successes over the last 31 days and don't plan on stopping anytime soon. I'm officially here for the long haul! IG & Twitter: Nikejerk
